title: Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS
text:
> Sports Little hit, big win; Royals beat Jays for 2-0 lead in ALCS Kansas City Royals' Alex Gordon hits an RBI double against the Toronto Blue Jays during the seventh inning in Game 2 of baseball's American League Championship Series against the Toronto Blue Jays on Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, in Kansas City, Mo. (AP Photo/Charlie Riedel)
